Package CommunicatingClasses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DownloadBatchIn
    This object stores the client's request to get a batch from the server
    DownloadBatchOut
    This class is an object that is built to send the batch to the client Gets all the information of the batch and sends it to the client's computer so the user can begin working on the batch
    GetFieldsIn
    This class is packages the information from the client Used by the server to return information about the fields in the project
    GetFieldsOut
    This object packages the information of the fields the user wants Returns information on all the fields requested
    GetProjectIn
    This class sends the request from the client to get info on the projects from the database
    GetProjectOut
    This class sends the information about the project back to the client
    SampleImageIn
    This class takes the information from the client to get a sample image from the database
    SampleImageOut
    This class packages the image url from the database and sends it to the client
    SearchInto
    This class sends to the server the information that is to be searched The server will use this information to respond to the client's request
    SearchOut
    This class is designed to package the information searched from the server Sends this information back to the client Uses a sub class Information to store the info
    SubmitBatchIn
    This class is designed to package all the information on the batch The client can now submit to the server
    SubmitBatchOut
    This class is designed to repsond to the user's batch summitted Let's the user know if the submission was successful or not
    ValidateUserIn
    This class sends the client's login information to the server
    ValidateUserOut
    This class informs the user if he/she was successfully logged into the program
